LOMP - Lua Open Music Player
By Daurnimator

Before running, you'll need to create a config file (called config in the lomp directory). See config.example.

If you run a debain based distro, head to the bottom of this file.

Dependencies:
	Lua >5.1.3					http://www.lua.org/
		download:				http://www.lua.org/ftp/lua-5.1.4.tar.gz
		can be obtained via:			apt-get install lua5.1

	Lgob (gstreamer module)				http://oproj.tuxfamily.org/wiki/doku.php?id=lgob
	
	Lua-iconv					http://luaforge.net/projects/lua-iconv/
		can be obtained via:			luarocks install lua-iconv
	
	LuaSocket					http://www.tecgraf.puc-rio.br/~diego/professional/luasocket/
		download:				http://luaforge.net/projects/luasocket/
		can be obtained via:			apt-get install liblua5.1-socket2
				or:			luarocks install luasocket
	
	LuaXMLRPC					http://www.keplerproject.org/luaxmlrpc/
		(now included)
		can be obtained (permanently) via:	apt-get install liblua5.1-xmlrpc0
		Depends on:
			LuaExpat			http://www.keplerproject.org/luaexpat/
				download:		http://luaforge.net/frs/?group_id=13
				can be obtained via:	apt-get install liblua5.1-expat0
						or:	luarocks install luaexpat
	
	LuaFileSystem					http://www.keplerproject.org/luafilesystem/
		can be obtained via: 			apt-get install liblua5.1-filesystem0
						or:	luarocks install luafilesystem

	Vstruct						http://www.funkyhorror.net/toxicfrog/projects/vstruct/
		(now included)

Optional Dependencies:
	luarocks					http://luarocks.org/
	
	lzlib	(for http gzip compression)		http://luaforge.net/projects/lzlib/
		can be obtained via: 			apt-get install liblua5.1-zip0
				or:			luarocks install lzlib

	md5						http://www.inf.puc-rio.br/~roberto/md5/md5-5/md5.html
		can be obtained via: 			apt-get install liblua5.1-md5-0
				or:			luarocks install md5

==> Systems with apt-get should be able to get most of the dependencies with:
apt-get install lua5.1 liblua5.1-socket2 liblua5.1-xmlrpc0 liblua5.1-expat0 liblua5.1-filesystem0 liblua5.1-zip0 liblua5.1-md5-0
apt-get install luarocks
luarocks install lua-iconv
apt-get install gstreamer0.10-plugins-base libgstreamer-plugins-base0.10-dev gstreamer0.10-plugins-good gstreamer0.10-plugins-bad gstreamer0.10-plugins-ugly

Lgob is a tricky install, and currently a very new library, you will have to install it manually. (see url above)
